author: Tales Azzoni / AP
title: Soccer Team From Wuhan Returns Home Nearly 4 Months After Leaving on Tour
description: The soccer team based in the epicenter of COVID-19 in China is back home, nearly four months after it left for a tour and got stuck abroad.
content:
(MADRID) — The soccer team based in the epicenter of the coronavirus pandemic in China is back home, nearly four months after it left for a preseason tour and got stuck abroad.
